include-tidy: error: "X": invalid value for --comment-style/-s; must be one of "//", "/*", or "none"

$ include-tidy -Xtidy --comment-symbols
include-tidy: error: "--comment-symbols/-S" requires an argument

$ include-tidy -Xtidy --comment-symbols=
include-tidy: error: "--comment-symbols/-S" requires an argument

$ include-tidy -Xtidy --comment-symbols=X
